summary: A cute elf preset and head mesh for race menu.
descriptionHtml:
A cute elf preset and head mesh for race menu.

In the image i'm using [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90801]Marla skin[/url], apachiiskyhair and mikan eyes, but the downloadable version don't need this mods.

                                 [img]https://i.imgur.com/bp6ImbF.jpg[/img]

Using:
Open Race menu

[b]sculpt > import head > volnutt cute elf[/b]
[b]presets > load preset > volnutt cute elf[/b]
author: VolnuttFallout
